Modernland Plans 802 Billion Rupiah Rights Offer, Director Says

-- B y   B e r n i   M o e s t a f a
-- 
2011-10-24T02:52:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-24/modernland-plans-802-billion-rupiah-rights-offer-director-says.html
PT Modernland Realty plans to raise
about 802 billion rupiah ($90 million) selling 3.2 billion
shares at 250 rupiah each in a rights offer this year, Finance
Director Freddy Chan said, confirming a report by Investor Daily
 Indonesia  today.  Proceeds from the sale will be used to acquire industrial
estates, Chan said by telephone.   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Berni Moestafa at 
 bmoestafa@bloomberg.net  